+
+For instant activation without rebuild:
+
+### Cloudflare Page Rule
+
+1. Go to Cloudflare Dashboard ‚Üí Page Rules
+2. Create rule: `yourdomain.com/*`
+3. Setting: **Forwarding URL** (302 Temporary Redirect)
+4. Destination: `yourdomain.com/maintenance.html`
