+
+1. ‚úÖ Keep current implementation for development
+2. Before production launch:
+   - [ ] Implement backend verification endpoints
+   - [ ] Test with real tokens
+   - [ ] Document bypass procedure for emergencies
+3. Optional: Add Cloudflare as instant fallback
